description: The Lab Food truck is a combo of Catifsh Connection & Lil Cajun's Grill & Sports. We are ready to hit the streets of Dallas and spread some cajun love!!!We have taken "Food Truck" to a different level. We are based out of Oak Cliff, TX and have combined two of our well known neighborhood resteraunts Catfish Connection & Lil Cajun's and have made them MOBILE!!!! Be on the look out for us on a street near YOU!!!
name: The Lab Food Truck
